Description: An iterative edge collapse-based simplification strategy for 
	triangular surface grids with distributed data. For the selection of the
	edge to contract at each iteration, an edge cost function is introduced,
	acconting for geometric and statistical considerations. The library can 
	handle both genus zero and higher genus surfaces.
